        <PHON kindOf="standard">saka maŋʦəz imaza; sitavaʎ piʦua qaqəRəŋan nua mamazaŋiʎan.</PHON>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="eng">So it came here and was set up by the chief’s bed.</TRANSL>
